node.text: @brooksanddunn and @realtravistritt tonight with my girl! Love me some good country music and waited 30 years to see Travis live! Thank you @iriscanterbury #countrymusic #livelife #blessed #soulmate #concert #musiclover

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 𝗗𝗮𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗯𝘂𝗿𝘆 in Pathfinder School Worldwide with @corporalscorner.

node.text: This is a shot of a recent raised bed made for video by @corporalscorner, if you are not subscribed to his YT channel you are missing some great content using simple tools to do some nice builds. Being the lead Instructor at #thepathfinderschoolllc he uses our teaching mentality in every video and they are packed with small tidbits of excellent information #bushcraft #toolheavy #the5cs #bushcraft101 #getoutside #staydirty #davecanterbury

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 𝗗𝗮𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗯𝘂𝗿𝘆 in Ohio with @ledlenserusa, and @bluetti_official.

node.text: My review of the Bluetti AC200 is now live on YT #solarpower #power #offroad #mobilepower #bluetti #getoutside #roadtrip #camping

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 𝗗𝗮𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗯𝘂𝗿𝘆 in Ohio with @morakniv, @selfrelianceoutfitters, and @davidfriars.

node.text: A chuckbox can take on many forms, this small kit covers everything I need for camp cooking on the road. We are currently developing an inclusive kit for one of my favorite Sponsor companies, I can’t wait to show you the results! #offroad #campcooking #getoutside #overlanding #jeeplife #davecanterbury

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by 𝗗𝗮𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗯𝘂𝗿𝘆 on August 31, 2021 tagging @leathermantools, @ledlenserusa, @morakniv, and @deckedusa.

node.text: The removable trays in the front of the @deckedusa system allow storage of small and quick access items to make truck organizations much less of a chore, with everything contained and easy to get at when needed it has become one of the favorite pieces of my Gladiator build! #jeeplife #offroad #getoutside #davecanterbury

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 𝗗𝗮𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗯𝘂𝗿𝘆 in Pathfinder School Worldwide. May be an image of food and nature.

node.text: Nice bloom over the last couple weeks here in SE Ohio #mushrooms #mushroomhunters #getoutside #foraging #staydirty #fungi #davecanterbury

node.text: A few projects from one student over the weekend in the BC 101. Notice the Spoon made specifically for also reaching the 90 degree angle of a Bush-pot when serving food. Small design considerations make a world of difference in overall usability in reality. #bushcraft #carving #woodcraft #thepathfinderschoolllc #davecanterbury #staydirty
